<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>A ghoulbane is perhaps the finast weapon a Pali can weild 1hs combined with a great sheild can out weigh any 2hs weapon out there. But do not oner pay for it wiat for a good deal like I did myself I picked one up for only 1700pp. Remember we can keep the prices down by not paying those high prices. Keep that in mind when u decide to start looking for one . And I suggest pay no more than 2kpp. The deals are out there be patient.</font></td></tr></table>
